              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 461,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Effects with this trait can affect creatures with spiritual essence and might deal spirit damage. A creature with this trait is defined by its spiritual essence. Spirit creatures often lack a material form.",
